divs: Sighting Detailson 06-15-2013 at 10:20pm in mabton washington yakima county me and my brother were bbq some meat it was just after sun set and was dark we noticed a bright light in the ski it was comeing from west to east in a straight line i think about 1000ft high. we watched it for about 2 or 3 min it passed right over us it made no noise what so ever just a bright light passing bi.it passed over mabton heading toward prosser, i never seen anything like that i just had to report it.
